icon.description: The name of the icon on the left, or the link to the image (absolute address is recommended for local files)
icon.description_zh: 左侧图标名称，或者图片链接(本地文件建议使用绝对地址)

border.description: Whether to display the lower border

center.description: Whether the content is vertically centered (mainly for the value part on the right)
center.description_zh: 内容是否垂直居中(主要是针对右侧的value部分)

url.description: The URL address to which you will be redirected

linkType.description: The route method of the uView encapsulation is used internally, and the operation may be intercepted
linkType.description_zh: 链接跳转的方式，内部使用的是uView封装的route方法，可能会进行拦截操作

clickable.description: Whether to turn on click feedback (as if you click with a gray background)
clickable.description_zh: 是否开启点击反馈(表现为点击时加上灰色背景)

isLink.description: Whether to show the arrow on the right and turn on click feedback
isLink.description_zh: 是否展示右侧箭头并开启点击反馈

required.description: Whether to display a required asterisk in the form state (this component may be embedded in the input component)
required.description_zh: 是否显示表单状态下的必填星号(此组件可能会内嵌入input组件)

arrowDirection.description: 右侧箭头的方向，可选值为：left，up，down
arrowDirection.description_zh: 右侧箭头的方向，可选值为：left，up，down

rightIconStyle.description: The style of the arrow icon on the right

size.description: The size of the unit, optionally large
size.description_zh: 单位元的大小，可选值为large

stop.description: Click on cell to prevent the event from propagating
stop.description_zh: 点击cell是否阻止事件传播

name.description: Identifier to be used to return in the click event
name.description_zh: 标识符，用于在click事件中进行返回

events.name: click
events.description: Triggered when you click on the cell list

slots.name: title
slots.description: If you want to customize the content of the title part on the left, do not define the title parameter or assign null values
slots.description_zh: 自定义左侧标题部分的内容，如需使用，请勿定义title参数，或赋值null即可

slots.name: value
slots.description: Customize the content of the title section on the right, if you need to use it, do not define the value parameter, or assign the value null
slots.description_zh: 自定义右侧标题部分的内容，如需使用，请勿定义value参数，或赋值null即可

slots.name: icon
slots.description: Customize the icon on the left

slots.name: right-icon
slots.description: To customize the content of the icon on the right, you need to set arrow to false for it to work
slots.description_zh: 自定义右侧图标内容，需设置arrow为false才起作用

slots.name: label
slots.description: To customize the label content, you must also set use-label-slot to true
slots.description_zh: 自定义label内容，需同时设置use-label-slot为true
